The breakfast which is included is European style, breads, juice and coffee and some sliced meats and cheese.	Breakfast with fresh rolls and pots of hot coffee and milk are fine, and yogurt and orange juice and sometimes meat and cheese and fruit round out this good start to the day.	Breakfast was basic and Italian style...just good coffee and brioche/bread, but I was happy with this, and if you're not, there are great cafes within minutes of the hotel, which has one of the very best loctions in Rome.	A simple breakfast comes with the room, bread, juice, coffee/tea, but if you are looking for something more you will need to go out.